    "description": "This Indonesian-style dish is smaller in size but packs a punch. You'll fry meat-free mince with sambal oelek, then pile it into lettuce cups with brown rice, courgette and carrot. Plate up and dig in. Smaller portion providing 2 of your 5-a-day, a source of fibre and high in protein.",
