    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Rinse your<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain, return it to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and keep covered until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/indonesian-style-meat-free-mince-and-brown-rice-lettuce-cups/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>meat-free mince</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to brown all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/indonesian-style-meat-free-mince-and-brown-rice-lettuce-cups/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail, peel and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail and grate your <strong>courgette[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>finely</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/indonesian-style-meat-free-mince-and-brown-rice-lettuce-cups/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once browned, transfer the<strong> meat-free mince</strong> to a clean mixing bowl, reserve the pan</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and mix to combine</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/indonesian-style-meat-free-mince-and-brown-rice-lettuce-cups/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat, and once hot add the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>carrot </strong>and <strong>courgette </strong>and cook for 2 min</p><p>Return the<strong> meat-free mince</strong> to the pan, reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for a further 3 min, then remove from the heat, add your <strong>sambal oelek</strong> and give everything a good mix up - this is your <strong>sambal meat-free mince</strong></p><p>Cover to keep warm until serving</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/indonesian-style-meat-free-mince-and-brown-rice-lettuce-cups/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Separate the<strong> outer leaves</strong> and arrange them on a plate</p><p>Shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/indonesian-style-meat-free-mince-and-brown-rice-lettuce-cups/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> through the sambal meat-free mince \u2013 this is your <strong>Indonesian-style meat-free mince</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/indonesian-style-meat-free-mince-and-brown-rice-lettuce-cups/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>To build your lettuce boats, top each <strong>lettuce leaf</strong> with a layer of <strong>cooked rice</strong> and some <strong>Indonesian-style meat-free mince</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
